title: Nashville Explosion Latest: FBI Scours Home of Person of Interest in Bombing
author: Austin Kellerman
comment: The bigger story is the massive communications blackout that is still going on. I still can't get through on the phone to my buddy down there.
I think it is far better to be an interesting person than a person of interest.
Why in the hell would we trust anything that the FBI is doing? Absolute BS.
This restaurant owner 100% had his insurance paid, he is thrilled lol
FBI? ATF? well, i guess this will never get solved. 50/50 they pin it on an innocent person.
description: Federal agents converged Saturday on the home of a possible person of interest in the explosion that rocked downtown Nashville as investigators scoured hundreds of tips and leads in the blast that damaged dozens of buildings on Christmas morning. WKRN report from 6pm Saturday night.
